                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280529-253-off1395 t18280529-253-cd1396"></join>, 1 gallon of porter, value 1s. 2d., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18280529-253-victim1366" type="victimName">
                        Henry 
